---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Destape de cañerías en Las Condes 24/7 | Expertos Certificados | Llegada en 30 min | Destape Rápido" 
    description="Destape de cañerías y alcantarillado en Las Condes. Servicio premium para casas y edificios, sin romper, con maquinaria eléctrica. Urgencias 24/7 y llegada en 30 minutos."
>
    <!-- Custom Styles for Zone Page -->
    <style slot="head">
        .bg-grid-pattern {
            background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 30px 30px;
        }

        .hero-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
        }

        .text-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #60a5fa, #22d3ee);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
    </style>

    <header class="relative py-24 overflow-hidden hero-gradient">
        <!-- Background Decor -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-30"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-12 opacity-10 blur-3xl">
            <div class="w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
             <div class="mb-6">
                 <div class="bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-sm inline-block px-4 rounded-full border border-white/10">
                    <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Zonas', href: '/zonas' }, { label: 'Urbano', href: '/zonas/urbano' }, { label: 'Las Condes', href: '#' }]} />
                 </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <div class="text-white">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-400/20 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 text-blue-300">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>
                        <span>Zona de Cobertura Exclusiva</span>
                    </div>

                    <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight tracking-tight">
                        Destapes en <br>
                        <span class="text-gradient">Las Condes</span>
                    </h1>

                    <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-xl leading-relaxed font-light">
                        Servicio premium de destape de alcantarillado y cañerías. Llegamos a tu domicilio en <strong>30 minutos</strong>. Técnicos certificados y maquinaria que no ensucia ni rompe.
                    </p>

                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-8">
                        <a href="tel:+56930153632"
                            class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white text-lg font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/30 transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 text-center flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i> Urgencia 24/7
                        </a>
                        <a href="#cobertura"
                            class="bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/10 text-white text-lg font-semibold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl transition flex items-center justify-center gap-2 backdrop-blur-sm">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-map"></i> Ver Mapa
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-6 border-t border-white/10">
                         <div>
                            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">30 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-400">min</span></div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Tiempo llegada</div>
                         </div>
                         <div>
                            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">24/7</div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Disponibilidad</div>
                         </div>
                         <div>
                            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">100%</div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Garantizado</div>
                         </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="hidden lg:block relative">
                     <!-- Image Card Effect -->
                     <div class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-white/10 transform rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition duration-500">
                        <img src="/images/camio-haciendo-servicio-en-la-calle.webp" alt="Camión Destape Rápido en Las Condes" class="w-full h-auto object-cover">
                        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 to-transparent p-8">
                            <p class="text-white font-bold text-lg"><i class="fa-solid fa-truck-fast text-blue-400 mr-2"></i> Unidades en ruta por Av. Las Condes</p>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
             <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
                <div class="p-8 md:p-12">
                    <div class="text-center mb-10">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Servicios Disponibles en Las Condes</h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-500">Atendemos casas, departamentos, oficinas y recintos comerciales en toda la comuna.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 shrink-0">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-toilet"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg">Destape de WC</h3>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Sin desmontar el artefacto. Solución limpia y desinfectada.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 shrink-0">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-sink"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg">Destapado de Lavaplatos</h3>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Eliminación de grasa y restos de comida con máquina eléctrica.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                         <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 shrink-0">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-building"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg">Verticales de Edificios</h3>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Mantención preventiva y correctiva para comunidades.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 shrink-0">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-water"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg">Piletas y Desagües</h3>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Limpieza de resumideros de patio, logia y baños.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-blue-600 p-8 text-center text-white">
                    <p class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">¿Tienes una emergencia ahora mismo?</p>
                    <a href="tel:+56930153632" class="inline-block bg-white text-blue-600 font-extrabold py-3 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-blue-50 transition transform hover:-translate-y-1">Llamar al +56 9 3015 3632</a>
                </div>
             </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
